    background: {fileID: 1999687876383525248, guid: 92e7a4a8d7018704b8a3e1f52543fea4, type: 3}
    lines:
    - Ahh.. the taste of coffe. You always liked it.
    - '"Coffe, coffe is my drink, if I don''t get it, I can''t think" - this words
